Invocation Name: movie picker
des: Have you ever had problems picking a movie rental to watch ? Let Alexa make the decision!! From "action" to "comedy" etc, simply say Alexa, "Open", "Start" or "Launch" movie picker and Alexa will pick out a movie category for you. Just say "what should i pick for movies?" and you are set to go!!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
